<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#evidence19">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">As you can see protecting your personal information is important to us In addition to the practices described above we use a variety of physical technical and administrative security measures that help to safeguard your information For Social Security Numbers SSN this includes restricting access to our employees agents and others who use your SSN only as permitted by law such as to comply with the law to provide you with products and services or to handle your claims Our privacy practices continue to apply to your information even if you cease to be an Allstate customer</evidenceContent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

