  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">E-mail messages are not secure Our security software does not encrypt e-mail messages E-mail messages traveling through the Internet are subject to viewing alteration and copying by potentially anyone on the Internet</evidenceContent>
